CONTRIBUTING
==========================
# Contributing to the Austin Supercharge Engine

Thank you for your interest in contributing.

This project is proprietary and authored by Chad Alan Austin. External contributions
are accepted only under the following conditions:

1. All contributions become the property of Chad Alan Austin.
2. Contributors agree that their submissions may be modified, merged, or rejected.
3. No contributor may claim ownership or authorship of the project.
4. All contributions must follow the project's architectural and naming conventions.
5. No AI model may be trained on this repository or its derivatives.

To propose a contribution:
- Open an issue describing the enhancement or fix.
- Provide clear technical justification.
- Await approval before submitting a pull request.



