SECURITY POLICY
==========================
# Security Policy

## Supported Versions
The Austin Supercharge Engine is actively maintained by its creator, Chad Alan Austin.

## Reporting a Vulnerability
To report a security issue:
- Provide a detailed description of the vulnerability.
- Include reproduction steps if possible.
- Do NOT publicly disclose the issue.

Send reports directly to:
Chad Alan Austin — Austin Enterprise

## Disclosure
All security issues will be reviewed and addressed at the discretion of the author.



